- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is the most likely category as the paper deals with numerical methods for approximating roots of polynomials. 
- cs.SC (Symbolic Computation) is also likely as the paper discusses algorithms for computing roots of polynomials. 
- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is relevant as the paper considers the geometric location of roots in its analysis. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses the complexity of the algorithm in terms of the degree of the polynomial and the separation of the roots.
